Hacienda Bella Realty & Property Management 

Equal Opportunity Housing 

Come see this beautiful 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home located in the highly desired San Lucas subdivision with quick access to the freeway to be anywhere in minutes. This home features an open airy floor plan, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, tile floors throughout the common areas, ceiling fans, master bath with dual sinks, large master closet, 2 car garage and spacious low care back yard with pavers. Beautiful community with parks, dog parks, walking paths and much, much more. This unit will not last long. If you are interested call text, email or schedule your viewing. Showings available Monday-Sunday 6am-7:30PM

Monthly Rent $2,499
Renter's insurance is required or $20.00 insurance waiver fee per month will apply or pay a $20 renter's insurance waiver fee.

Hacienda Bella Realty Charges a $149.00 admin fee. 

Non-Refundable Cleaning Fee $500.00 

Non-Refundable Pet Fee $250.00 per pet (Pet Restrictions Apply/ 2 Pet limit). No aggressive breeds allowed; no pet deemed aggressive by management will be allowed. 

Applicable Security 

Deposit $2,499.00 on approved application. (Additional deposit may be required depending on application results). 

Ask about our $0.00 deposit special. 

We have partnered with Obligo and Rhino, 2 different companies which provide 2 different options for the zero-deposit special. Here is some information from Obligo. 

Welcome to Your Deposit-Free Home
Make your rental process as simple as checking in and
out of a hotel. Your property has partnered with Obligo to
allow qualified renters to skip paying a security deposit.
Enjoy Financial Flexibility
Use your deposit cash to invest, save or spend.
Move in right from your phone. No need to go to the bank.
No waiting for your deposit back via snail mail!
Instantly Qualify
Obligo has several methods to instantly qualify for deposit free
living. Most renters will qualify by connecting one US
bank account.

Learn more at myobligo.com
You are Still Accountable
Through the Obligo platform, you authorize your property
manager to charge you up to your security deposit amount
for any damages or missed rent. Any balance can be repaid
in installments.
You maintain the right to dispute charges with your property
manager - just like a traditional deposit.
Deposit-Free Living Starts Here
When it is time to pay the security deposit you will receive a
secure link to Obligo with more details about our service.
If you did not receive an invite or if you have any questions,
Obligo charges a small fee for the service.
There is no need to tie up your funds. The days of your
security deposit money being locked away, collecting
dust, are over.

As for Rhino, with this program instead of submitting a deposit equivalent to one month's rent which in this case would be $2,499.00, tenant would receive an invitation from us via email to sign up for Rhino Surety Bond. The tenant would apply for the option and pay a monthly fee, Rhino Surety Bond will quote the monthly payment before signing up. There is a one-time $149.00 Obligo or Rhino Surety Bond Option fee required for these two options.

To Qualify for this property, Ideal Tenant shall have: good rental history: No- evictions 7 yrs. older, owe no money to any landlord or management company or utility company. 

Good Credit: Minimum score is 550 (Some exceptions may be possible with owner approval) 
Criminal Background: Per HUD Guidelines: Not only must Applicant have acceptable credit history, additionally, all Applicants must meet our Criminal History Criteria. Applicants that are registered sex offenders will be denied. Applicants must have no felony convictions less than 10 years old that involve violent crimes against persons or property, including but not limited to murder, arson, kidnapping, assault, bomb related offenses, robbery or burglary, terrorism OR that involve the manufacturing or distribution of drugs in any manner. All other felony convictions must be more than 5 years old. Conviction of any drug related offenses involving possession only, or alcohol related offenses where no one was permanently injured or killed, must be at least 2 years old. Successful completion of any felony sentence at least 2 years ago and no new criminal activity for at least 2 years before this application is also required. No Applicant with any outstanding warrants or crime that is awaiting trial will be accepted. If the Applicant would like management to review additional information regarding the felony conviction or the current arrest or warrant as part of their rental application, the Applicant is permitted to submit that information to management along with their application and Management will review that information on a case-by-case basis. 

No Evictions must not owe monies to any other landlord/management company. (Ask about our eviction forgiveness program.) Must have verifiable gross monthly income of $6,050 or more combined. 
Proof of income is required. Every adult 18yrs or older interested in moving in must apply. 

Application fee is $40.00 per adult. Application fees are Non-Refundable. 
Listed and professionally managed by Hacienda Bella Realty & Property Management 
 

**Equal Housing Opportunity** Apply Online: 

Step 1.
Step 2. Send in PDF format copies of every adult ID's and the last 2 check stubs for your proof of income. Make sure to submit the application payment online otherwise we cannot process the application. If you are looking for immediate move-in please purchase and pay with money order, online payments take 3 days to settle/process. PLEASE DO NOT APPLY if you do not have the full application fee(s). 

Step 3. Please text or call us once you have submitted and paid for your applications so that we can start processing them. This property allows self guided viewing without an appointment. Contact for details.
